@Date:	07-JAN-1972
@Time Start:	15:00
@Situation:	Peter is asleep when Lois PAT arrive. Mother brings him into the living room half asleep wrapped in his blanket. he sits in a chair , groggy for a few minutes then Patsy starts getting toys out of bag and Peter climbs down from chair to join Patsy on floor. Peter still has a bad cold.
